name: Cat Water Fountain
description: Water fountain for cats to drink out of. Made of stainless steel. The dynamic water flow helps attract pet cats to drink, providing a ton of health benefits. Comes with three filters (additional filters bought separately).

name: Capybara Plush
description: Weighted capybara plush that can be heated up in the microwave. Keeps heat for hours. French lavendar scented. Weighs 2lbs. Promotes better quality sleep.

name: Roku Streaming Device
description: Roku HD Streaming Device. Comes with rechargeable voice remote.

name: SpongeBob DoodleBob Hat
description: Hat with DoodleBob (from SpongeBob) on it. Adjustable snapback. Super stylish.

name: Silent Hill HD Collection
description: Video game for Xbox 360 containing ports of Silent Hill 2 (including Restless Dreams) and Silent Hill 3. Both titles re-mastered to HD at 720p. Updated in-game voiceover and enhanced soundtrack.

name: Scooby Doo Magnet
description: Magnet with Scooby Doo graphic consisting of the entire gang with a green funky background. Good for fridge or locker doors.

name: Green Spotted Sea Monster Rubber Duck
description: A rubber duck that has green spots and is "sea monster" theme. Good to talk through coding problems with.

name: Horse Head Mask
description: Brown horse head mask made of latex. Large enough to fit most adults and kids heads. See through the mask's mouth and nose holes. Perfect for Halloween.

name: Chobani Coconut Yogurt
description: Low-fat greek yogurt with coconut blend. Yummy!

name: Bose Noise Cancelling Headphones
description: Acoustic noise cancelling over ear black headphones by Bose. Wired connectivity.
